然佢要知道你既身份證號碼同中英文全名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/xz7tbmcbmkj31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fxz7tbmcbmkj31.jpg&h=b31178b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/hb6qnadvjkj31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fhb6qnadvjkj31.jpg&h=d5f45a58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7af8e1c6d4d3838dd84c52053c43ccf1bed087b5","tid":1518943,"uid":130898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:58:40.000Z","msg":"依d先係合理價<br />\n樓價應該delay下跌 <br />\n應該都係偏遠地區跌先"},{"pid":"6b334a37692977fd498b7b020bf9be877b483ba0","tid":1518943,"uid":15605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:01:30.000Z","msg":"太貴了，支持攬炒，月租800<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}